title: Edges are not responsive, so I have to go in and out of the app inorder to use the icons in the edge
content:
Edges are not responsive, so I have to go in and out of the app inorder to use the icons in the edge.

I removed screen gaurd and back case and still had the issue.

I had this issue form the time I bought the phone. Due to pandemic I never contacted support until now

How can I claim under warranty
